name: MALO SERIES
description:
Our motto is "unique pieces for unique people" which means that only a limited quantity of each bracelet is made. We all know how much we hate seeing EVERYONE wear the same thing, so why have something everyone else has? 

Be part of an individualistic society. Be you, be part of Right Wrist Society.

100% handcrafted
